    "title": "Distribution Manager Vacancy at DTDC - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at DTDC. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Distribution Manager to strengthen our Meerut-based team.\n\nAbout DTDC:\nDTDC is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DTDC!",
